{"abstract":[{"text":"Configure PixieCacheKit for optimized image caching.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Configure caching settings at app launch to optimize image loading and storage management.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Configure Caching Options","anchor":"Configure-Caching-Options","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To get started, import PixieCacheKit at the beginning of your SwiftUI app file. In the initializer of your "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"App"},{"type":"text","text":" struct, configure the caching options using configuration methods:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["import SwiftUI","import PixieCacheKit","","@main","struct MyApp: App {","    init() {","        \/\/ Configure to use a custom directory for file-based image caching.","        PixieCacheKit.configure(directoryName: \"MyAppCache\", imageFormat: .jpeg)","      ","      ","        \/\/ Use a specific memory limit for image caching.","        PixieCacheKit.configure(memoryLimit: 100)","    }","","    var body: some Scene {","        WindowGroup {","            ContentView()","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If not configured explicitly, PixieCacheKit defaults to using ‘PixieImageCache’ as the cache directory name, ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".jpeg"},{"text":" as the image format, and file manager storage for caching.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Note","style":"note","type":"aside"}]}],"kind":"article","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pixiecachekit\/getting-started"]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/PixieCacheKit\/documentation\/PixieCacheKit\/Getting-Started","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/PixieCacheKit\/documentation\/PixieCacheKit"]]},"metadata":{"role":"article","modules":[{"name":"PixieCacheKit"}],"title":"Getting Started","roleHeading":"Article"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://PixieCacheKit/documentation/PixieCacheKit":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A simple image caching package for SwiftUI."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/PixieCacheKit\/documentation\/PixieCacheKit","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pixiecachekit","type":"topic","title":"PixieCacheKit"}}}